":"2025-12-12T13:57:01"},{"id":"019b1145-99f6-71e9-a8bd-a71fd2d92313","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":23067,"content":"北京最重要的是没有户口吧，没户口不让孩子高考，车牌也有限制。","createdAt":"2025-12-12T14:35:32"},{"id":"019b118d-eec4-70d1-ac30-107761cf4956","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":875,"content":"北京落户门槛低了，可以走人才引进，再不济积分落户，超过40岁再去北京，社保在北京都交不上了","createdAt":"2025-12-12T15:54:33"},{"id":"019b11ae-34a2-70fb-8a54-dcf70cc3e950","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":25332,"content":"你主要得考虑怎么留下啊，在北京买不起房最后不还是得回来","createdAt":"2025-12-12T16:29:48"},{"id":"019b12be-116b-72dd-a9fc-b026501b129b","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":875,"content":"回来咋地了，回来了，领北京标准版的退休金不香嘛","createdAt":"2025-12-12T21:26:44"},{"id":"019b8c1d-9679-7298-a3e2-9d44a21ef416","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":28081,"content":"趁年轻，建议去北上广深杭这几个城市试试，不要在济南，如果十年后赚够了钱回来养老可以，赚钱的话，济南真不行","createdAt":"2026-01-05T11:05:07"},{"id":"019b8c49-f082-70bf-bace-cf6eab50ac05","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1049,"content":"太离谱了吧，兄弟","createdAt":"2026-01-05T11:53:34"},{"id":"019b8c4a-ee2d-7155-87f6-88b229d140ee","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1049,"content":"这个兄弟是个明白人","createdAt":"2026-01-05T11:54:39"}]